## Crossmap
# Best way is to install via conda
# package is here https://bioconda.github.io/recipes/crossmap/README.html

# So, first install conda...
# for ubuntu 16.04, see https://medium.com/@menuram1126/how-to-install-anaconda-on-ubuntu-16-04-538009ca7936

# Setup bioconda channels
# https://bioconda.github.io/index.html#set-up-channels

conda config --add channels defaults
conda config --add channels bioconda
conda config --add channels conda-forge

# Then use conda o install Crossmap.py
conda install crossmap
